profile_positions.description:
'' From Childhood Dream to Enterprise Family Business ''

More than thirty years ago, Ben Mandemakers started his kitchen business in a small shed behind his parents' house. Mandemakers Kitchens has since grown into the leading business in the Benelux. At the time, Ben had one main motivation; he had to and would prove that things could be done differently in the kitchen industry. We can now confidently say that he has fully proven that.

Quality and customer-friendliness have always come first at Ben Mandemakers. And of course those two factors were closely followed by competitive prices and a hell of a service. Consumers quickly learned to appreciate Ben's approach.

In this way, every customer provided beautiful word-of-mouth advertising. The first employees soon arrived; people who were just as fanatic and enthusiastic as Ben himself. And the nice thing is that those same people still work for the company.

Despite the enormous size of his company - there are now eight branches - Ben is still intensively involved in the daily business. For example, he is very keen on the quality of everything he purchases. So critical that the entire procurement is still under his direct responsibility. Fortunately, Ben is now supported by his eldest son Stefan.

profile_positions.description:
BSG Contact has been known for more than 50 years as a market leader in facilitating commercial customer contact for the leading organizations within the Benelux. From our offices in Almere, Arnhem, Utrecht, Antwerp and Ghent, more than 600 agents are committed to various challenging commercial projects every day. BSG Contact is regarded as a benchmark within the market of commercial customer contact. Through a distinctive proposition and the constant provision of high-quality commercial training to our agents, BSG Contact can continuously offer high quality to its relations and we offer our agents an inspiring environment in which personal development is central.

Why BSG?

BSG Contact works for prominent players in various market segments. We opt for a proposition where each project is unique and tailor-made to our clients. We see our sales as an integral part of your commercial system and work with regular partners to meet all facets of a commercial proposition at a multi-channel level. A business case is always our starting point to ensure that the chances of a successful collaboration are optimal. For both B2B and B2C, BSG Contact offers years of experience with Top 500 companies in a wide variety of processes.
